"title": "8297: love, for God",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8297",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture teaches believers to love God and shows how such love should be expressed in worship and practical service.</p>\n<h2>Believers' response to God's love</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:19\">1JN 4:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:7-Deut7:8\">DEU 7:7–7:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps116:1\">PSA 116:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:16\">JHN 15:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:4-Eph2:5\">EPH 2:4–2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:10\">1JN 4:10</a></p>\n<h2>Love for God is commanded</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:37-Matt22:38\">MAT 22:37–22:38</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:29-Mark12:30\">MRK 12:29–12:30</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:5\">DEU 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:12\">DEU 10:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:1\">DEU 11:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh22:5\">JOS 22:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh23:11\">JOS 23:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:23\">PSA 31:23</a></p>\n<h2>Loving God involves loving Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:42\">JHN 8:42</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:42\">JHN 5:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:23\">JHN 15:23</a></p>\n<h2>Expressing love for God</h2>\n<h3>Delight in worship and in God's house</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:4\">PSA 27:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps26:8\">PSA 26:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps43:4\">PSA 43:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps65:4\">PSA 65:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps84:2\">PSA 84:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps122:1\">PSA 122:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps122:6\">PSA 122:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:46-Acts2:47\">ACT 2:46–2:47</a></p>\n<h3>Love for God's word</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:97\">PSA 119:97</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:2\">PSA 1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:7-Ps19:8\">PSA 19:7–19:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:10\">PSA 19:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:16\">PSA 119:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:35\">PSA 119:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:72\">PSA 119:72</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:163\">PSA 119:163</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:16\">JER 15:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:3\">EZK 3:3</a></p>\n<h3>Self-sacrifice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:33\">LUK 14:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:15-John21:17\">JHN 21:15–21:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1\">ROM 12:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:8\">PHP 3:8</a></p>\n<h3>Giving</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:3\">1CH 29:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:2\">EXO 25:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:5\">EXO 35:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:6\">1CH 29:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:9\">1CH 29:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:4-2Cor8:5\">2CO 8:4–8:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:8\">2CO 8:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:7\">2CO 9:7</a></p>\n<h3>Obeying God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:3\">1JN 5:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:8\">PSA 40:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:15\">JHN 14:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:23\">JHN 14:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:14\">JHN 15:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:6\">2JN 1:6</a></p>\n<h3>Loving others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:21\">1JN 4:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:35\">JHN 13:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:12\">JHN 15:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:11\">1JN 4:11</a></p>\n<h2>The blessings of loving God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:15-John14:16\">JHN 14:15–14:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:23\">JHN 14:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:27\">JHN 16:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:8\">1PE 1:8</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of love for God and Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:1\">PSA 18:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:25\">PSA 73:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:7\">MAT 26:7</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:3\">MRK 14:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:3\">JHN 12:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:37\">LUK 2:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:47\">LUK 7:47</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:53\">LUK 24:53</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:16\">JHN 11:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:16\">JHN 21:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:13\">ACT 21:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:10\">HEB 6:10</a></p>",
